<t>The Point-to-Point Protocol (PPP)provides a standard method for transporting multi-protocol datagrams over point-to-point links.  PPP also defines an extensible Link Control Protocol.</t>
<t>This document defines a method for negotiating data compression over PPP links.</t></abstract></front>

